snippet.title: The Truth About Ivana Trump's Life Today
snippet.description:
Melania Trump has mostly stayed out of the spotlight during her time as First Lady, and she doesn’t seem to advise her husband much, but there is another woman who allegedly does — Donald’s first wife, Ivana Trump.

Born Ivana Zelnickova in then-Czechoslovakia, Ivana was married to Donald Trump from 1977 to 1992, when the future President’s highly-publicized affair with Marla Maples ended his marriage. However, Ivana claims she is still quite close with Donald, saying she calls him once a week to advise him. Is there any truth to this? Let’s take a look at what Ivana Trump’s life is like today.
